<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c2">(وَإِنْ يَرَوْا كِسْفًا مِنَ السَّمَاءِ سَاقِطًا يَقُولُوا سَحَابٌ مَرْكُومٌ (٤٤)</span> فَذَرْهُمْ حَتَّى يُلَاقُوا يَوْمَهُمُ الَّذِي فِيهِ يُصْعَقُونَ <span class="c2">(٤٥)</span> يَوْمَ لَا يُغْنِي عَنْهُمْ كَيْدُهُمْ شَيْئًا وَلَا هُمْ يُنْصَرُونَ <span class="c2">(٤٦)</span>) .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c2">(وَإِنْ يَرَوْا)</span> : قِيلَ: <span class="c2">«إِنْ»</span> عَلَى بَابِهَا.<span class="c5"> وَقِيلَ:</span> هِيَ بِمَعْنَى لَوْ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَ <span class="c2">(يَوْمَهُمُ)</span> : مَفْعُولٌ بِهِ. وَ <span class="c2">(يُصْعَقُونَ)</span> بِفَتْحِ الْيَاءِ،<span class="c5"> وَمَاضِيهِ:</span> صَعِقَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَيُقْرَأُ بِضَمِّهَا، وَمَاضِيهِ صَعِقَ،<span class="c5"> وَقِيلَ:</span> صَعُقَ مِثْلُ سَعُدَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَ <span class="c2">(يَوْمَ لَا يُغْنِي)</span> : بَدَلٌ مِنْ <span class="c2">«يَوْمِهِمْ»</span> .<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c2">(وَمِنَ اللَّيْلِ فَسَبِّحْهُ وَإِدْبَارَ النُّجُومِ (٤٩)</span>) .<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(وَإِدْبَارَ النُّجُومِ)</span> : مِثْلُ أَدْبَارِ السُّجُودِ، وَقَدْ ذُكِرَ فِي <span class="c2">«ق»</span> .<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>